{"tid":1553391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[搭你老母黨鐵] 908 由港島爬返屋企","createTime":"2019-09-08T14:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:26:13.000Z","uid":282280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05d46b7d0de6cd3204abbf37f6680488f702a9ef","tid":1553391,"uid":282280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"話說今日小妹一丁友出去行，<br />\n行到一半就收到4:45分前要散，<br />\n當時4:30，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8xLf03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8xLf03.png&h=3581c474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我就由果度行返落去遮打，<br />\n知道好多路都封左，<br />\n小妹<span style=\"color: red;\">途經</span>金鐘地鐵站，<br />\n果時金鐘仲有車行，<br />\n見到班老鼠都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUMPHMy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUMPHMy.jpg&h=c4001362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6atdTi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6atdTi.png&h=71827fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我就行去會展果頭搭<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巴士</span>，<br />\n加埋搵路時間，行左一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n架巴士係我住果頭既隔一個火車站，<br />\n食埋野再去等<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巴士</span><br />\n返屋企時長約3個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等車企到腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾方便都唔撚搭你垃圾黨鐵<br />\n吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">最後，多謝做人肉廣播既KMB哥哥姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"27108ce3dd5259ff9e03979aec9d79f675dae2e1","tid":1553391,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p